was to blame, the Pentagon's spokesman, Kenneth H. Bacon, said
simply, ``I don't think we fully understand yet.''
</P>
<P>
   A Gigantic Gathering Of World Leaders
</P>
<P>
   United Nations Secretary-General Kofi Annan called it ``a
remarkable convergence of views.'' When about 150 government
