 UNDATED: of rights.  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Then the costs began to rise again. Last week, the Kaiser
Foundation reported that between the spring of 1999 and the spring
of 2000, monthly premiums for employer-sponsored health insurance
