</P>
<P>
   OLY-NEW-SPORTS _ ATLANTA _ Since the Olympics began 104 years
ago with 43 events, the Games continue to change with the times.
Sydney will offer 300 events, including two new sports _ taekwondo
and triathlon _ and various additions and wrinkles to existing
sports. (Rosen, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
</P>
